Private Company firmographics can be found in the FactSet Entity API. The future plans of this service will include additional Private Markets data, such as Private Equity/Venture Capital. title: FactSet Private Markets API version: 1.0.0 servers: - description: Production url: https://api.factset.com/content security: - FactSetApiKey: [] - FactSetOAuth2: [] tags: - description: Retrieve Private Company Financials name: Financials - description: Retrieve Private Company Reference Data. name: Non-Periodic - description: Retrieve available Private Company fields, metrics, and ratios. name: Data Items paths: /factset-private-markets/v1/financials: get: description: | Returns Private Company Financials Information. operationId: getFinancials parameters: - description: | The requested FactSet Private Market Entity Identifier in XXXXXX-E format.

**Max Ids Limit set to 3000 in a single request**

*

Make note, GET Method URL request lines are also limited to a total length of 8192 bytes (8KB). In cases where the service allows for thousands of ids, which may lead to exceeding this request line limit of 8KB, its advised for any requests with large request lines to be requested through the respective \"POST\" method.
